{"tid":931454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國電信宣布移除 4G 網路華為設備　未來 5G 亦不用華為","createTime":"2018-12-07T05:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:29:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e54632da3ac795d00a9b67fa0ebdab6a97cbfb75","tid":931454,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/UK-HUAWEI-01_BtEKC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUK-HUAWEI-01_BtEKC_1200x0.png&h=d8045755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愈來愈多西方國家關注華為引發的安全隱憂。英國電信集團（BT Group）周三宣布，將在兩年內移除核心4G網路中的華為設備，並保證未來的核心5G網絡亦不會使用華為。<br />\n<br />\n英國電信集團表示，其固網核心未有使用華為設備。至於早前英國電信收購的英國最大流動網絡商EE，他們有使用華設備，亦將會移除。公司發言人形容，這做法是為了確保EE網絡與其他業務政策一致。<br />\n<br />\n英國電信集團亦表明，有關原則適用於下一代的網路發展，「因此，華為並不屬於我們5G核心設備供應商之內」。公司發言人強調華為仍然是重要的創新伙伴，公司在核心網絡以外的其他範疇，會繼續使用華為設備。<br />\n<br />\n近年多個西方國家都關注到華為引發的國家安全問題。新西蘭上月決定，禁止當地其中一家最大網絡供應商 Spark， 使用中國華為的 5G 設備。今年8月澳洲政府亦宣布禁止華為為其5G移動網絡提供設備，理由是存在遭受外國干預的風險。<br />\n<br />\n另外今日傳媒爆出消息指，華為首席財務官（CFO）孟晚舟，在周六（12月1日）在溫哥華國際機場被加拿大當局拘捕，並可能引渡至美國，因被懷疑違反了美國針對伊朗的制裁規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/英國電信宣布移除-4g-網路華為設備-未來-5g-亦不用華為/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4-4g-%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86-5g-%E4%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%2F&d=KSHrbrcZAjs90lyxCGdwe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3172e0fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4-4g-%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86-5g-%E4%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%2F&h=8292a2f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/英國電信宣布移除-4g-網路華為設備-未來-5g-亦不用華為/</a>"},{"pid":"e9a0e48a779cbba2e5b4b8019dbeec347f5efb67","tid":931454,"uid":168366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"你睇下堆港豬<br />\n個個走去用支那brand<br />\n呢度都大把呢d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca4c2d550e9ea92f32a156cc774be76bcea95b6","tid":931454,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"下一步，聯想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7615c96b9345dce61af2cbbd069e6e60c735469","tid":931454,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"相反老電嗰啲真係冇得救，快啲執柒咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8818df21c3cf83d4131bf03772d6a3a8ab7102","tid":931454,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c1b192db9cd06e8337e22c14a5aea46679e2eea","tid":931454,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7615c96b9345dce61af2cbbd069e6e60c735469","tid":931454,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"相反老電嗰啲真係冇得救，快啲執柒咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"傳過想賣畀大陸佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177dc9d6cbc424dc5120095e29379893a2302803","tid":931454,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c1b192db9cd06e8337e22c14a5aea46679e2eea","tid":931454,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7615c96b9345dce61af2cbbd069e6e60c735469","tid":931454,"uid":335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"相反老電嗰啲真係冇得救，快啲執柒咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"h